race.description: Bet Nation Same Race Multi 5Th Grade H
race.comment: WILLOW'S WITCH (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at Q Lakeside. Key player on best and worth another chance. FEDERAL ICEMAN (1) won again in another strong performance to make it two in a row, scoring by 1.75 lengths (21.93) at this track over 380m. Hard to fault his form and he makes plenty of appeal. HARA'S SERENA (5) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 380m behind Balt's Shadow (22.48) in a P5. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. HELIANTHE (8) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.

runners.name: Willow's Witch
